               <provenance>The name(s) of the original donor(s) has been
                     erased throughout the Ms. and replaced with the names of ʾAśrāta Māryām,
                     ʾAśrāta Ṣǝyon and Ṣǝge Dǝngǝl in the concluding supplication on 73vb. Their names and one more name have been also
                     added into the supplication formulas: ʾAśrāta Māryām (3ra, 40rb, 51rb-51va, 62rb, 62va, 65ra), ʾAśrāta Ṣǝyon (39va, 62ra, 62va, 65ra), Māryāmawit (31ra, 39vb, 63ra) and Ṣǝge Dǝngǝl (57vb, 61va, 64vb), in a secondary hand, in vivid
                     red.</provenance></history>
